<DocsLayout title="status" section="commands">
  <h1>status</h1>
  <p class="lead">Show managed worktree services.</p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>
  <pre><code>docktree status [flags]</code></pre>
  <p>Runs <code>docker compose ps</code> for the current worktree's project and displays container state.</p>

  <h2>Flags</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>Flag</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>-a, --all</code></td><td>Show status for all worktree instances in this repository</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Examples</h2>
  <pre><code>docktree status
docktree status --all</code></pre>
</DocsLayout>
